" Don't use abbreviations!  Spelling things out makes grepping easy.

" Load plugins using Pathogen. Don't worry if this bit doesn't make sense.
filetype off
call pathogen#runtime_append_all_bundles()
filetype indent plugin on
syntax on
set nocompatible

" That's all you need for a working Vim setup.

" Now set some directives...
" set incsearch         " find the next match as we type the search
" set hlsearch          " hilight searches by default
" ... etc

" And enable some plugins or -- better -- and add some of your own!
" Putting text before BUNDLE disables it: "no BUNDLE", "# BUNDLE", etc.

